summary: allows innkeepers to eat while working their shifts
descriptionHtml:
simply edits the innkeeper packages so they can randomly eat while they are sandboxing at work (which is like, 24/7)

drop the file in your skyrim data folder and make sure it is selected in your load order or mod organizer

requires dragonborn or the legendary edition

compatible with Sleeping Innkeepers
if you use Immersive Citizens AI Overhaul, this mod will have no effect on npc schedules while have already been improved
